<br>
There are also ruins to the east of the fort where various gorillas and skellies spawn.  About half will be blue to you.  That spot also has a &quot;safe&quot; area to med...a barren spot with burned out trees.<br>
<br>
Basically, stick to the northwest portion of BW and you will find plenty of blues to hunt at 53.  I've also found blues to the northeast but haven't found all the &quot;safe&quot; spots yet.<br>
<br>
Shaz<br>
