Just 3rd gate i was there from level 49 to 55.<br>
Easy Kill , Damn good exp, ok loot.<br>
<br>
Go invis to the bridge near the wizzis, go to the wall left.<br>
If the wandering Lottle not there cast pet.<br>
Wait for him, send pet. Kill him whit to sos or what ever.<br>
Move near the entrance wait there , next wizz come kill him.<br>
if the spawns broken you have the easyiest exp point ever.<br>
i sit near the entrance o nthe way and my pet guard near the small bridge , when he pops pet attack , nuke full exp most time, wait next one again. blabla<br>
