<br>
<br>
here s the XP table : <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://hackersquest.gomp.ch/html/xp/xpchart.html">XP chart Table</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
refering to this table for a Human Magician :<br>
at level 49 u need 10 000 000 approx xp to level .<br>
so lets say its god awesome XP and u gain 2 blue bub per hour<br>
so 10 000 000 / 25 = 400 000 xp / 30 minutes<br>
<br>
to get 55 u need from 49 to gain : 160 000 000 xp .<br>
so 160 000 000 * 30 / 400 000 = 12 000 minutes = 200 hours = 8.3 days ..<br>
<br>
and i guess like everybody u need to sleep in one entire week.<br>
unless you are one of those ghoul we use to met in norrath .....<br>
<br>
edit : forget to mention that was for a human mage . but its kinda the same for all other mage .<br>
