>
I stand off pretty far from the base of the ramp when there are 2 giants and I try to cast Lava Bolt. inch forward after each attempt to cast it. When it goes off back up fast. (Best to have already parked your pet back a ways). The giant takes a hit and stand there scratching his butt. Then you inch forward from right about where Bolt actually casted from till the giant agroes on ya. Then you run back to pet. This worked for me very well on those mornings when there was almost nobody in the zone but me. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Takes VERY little practice to get it down.<br>
